Pigments, the debut collaboration between New Orleans electro-revival dynamo Dawn Richard and multi-instrumentalist, producer, and composer Spencer Zahn.

"Pigments is a project about the power of self-expression through living art, through motion. It’s also a love letter to New Orleans, Louisiana.
